Package: surveyr
Title: A Package for Analysing Survey Responses
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Chris",
           family = "Brownlie",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "christopher.brownlie@education.gov.uk")
Description: A series of functions that speed up and simplify basic analysis of free text survey responses. 
             Functions for cleaning and anonymising data as well as generating tables of common words or n-grams, and
             sentiment or themes of responses.
             All functions are designed to be used in conjunction with a tidyverse workflow.
